
---

## **.gitignore**

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.env
*.venv
env/
venv/
ENV/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Python packages
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Model files
*.keras
*.h5
*.hdf5

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp